OL,3,COne in four university physics
OL,4,Cdepartments fear closure in next two
OL,5,Cyears ` poll
OL,7,FA quarter of UK university physics
OL,8,Fdepartment heads fear their units will
OL,9,Fbe shut down within the next two years
OL,10,Fdue to financial pressures, a survey
OL,11,Fhas found.
OL,13,FIn a survey by the Institute of
OL,14,FPhysics (IOP), most university physics
OL,15,Fheads of departments (84%) said they
OL,16,Fwere facing financial challenges or
OL,17,Fhad done so recently.
OL,19,FEight department heads (27%) said they
OL,20,Fexpected to face possible closure
OL,21,Fwithin the next two years.
