OL,3,COne in four university physics
OL,4,Cdepartments fear closure in next two
OL,5,Cyears ` poll
OL,7,FMore than four in five (83%) expected
OL,8,Fthere to be staff cuts within the next
OL,9,Ftwo years, and 60% were anticipating
OL,10,Fdegree courses closing in their
OL,11,Fdepartment.
OL,13,FIOP president Sir Keith Burnett,
OL,14,Fformer vice chancellor at the
OL,15,FUniversity of Sheffield and former
OL,16,Fchair of physics at the University of
OL,17,FOxford, said: "Just when we most need
OL,18,Fphysics graduates, researchers and
OL,19,Finnovators, the foundations of this
OL,20,Fecosystem are under the most severe
OL,21,Fthreat.
