OL,7,F"While we understand the pressures on
OL,8,Fpublic finances, it would be negligent
OL,9,Fnot to sound the alarm for a national
OL,10,Fcapability fundamental to our well-
OL,11,Fbeing, competitiveness and the defence
OL,12,Fof the realm.
OL,14,F"We are walking towards a cliff edge
OL,15,Fbut there is still time to avert a
OL,16,Fcrisis which would lead not just to
OL,17,Flost potential but to many physics
OL,18,Fdepartments shutting down altogether."
