OL,3,COne in four university physics
OL,4,Cdepartments fear closure in next two
OL,5,Cyears ` poll
OL,7,FThere are roughly 60 university
OL,8,Fphysics departments in the UK. IOP
OL,9,Freceived survey responses from 31 in
OL,10,Ftotal ` around half.
OL,12,FSome 79% said they were already facing
OL,13,For had recently had staff cuts in
OL,14,Ftheir departments.
OL,16,FMore than one in three (38%) said they
OL,17,Fhad considered mergers or
OL,18,Fconsolidation.
