OL,3,COne in four university physics
OL,4,Cdepartments fear closure in next two
OL,5,Cyears ` poll
OL,7,FIOP said the numbers of students
OL,8,Fstudying physics started to drop in
OL,9,F2021/22 after steady growth in the
OL,10,Fprevious decade.
OL,12,FUniversities across the UK are facing
OL,13,Ffinancial challenges, with many having
OL,14,Fannounced redundancies or cost-cutting
OL,15,Fmeasures. More than two in five
OL,16,Fforecast a deficit for 2024/25 in data
OL,17,Freleased in May.
