OL,7,FPhysics departments are vulnerable to
OL,8,Fthese growing financial pressures "due
OL,9,Fto the comparatively high teaching
OL,10,Fcosts of physics", the IOP said.
OL,12,FOne head of physics at a UK University
OL,13,Fsaid: "Our university has a #30
OL,14,Fmillion deficit. Staff recruitment is
OL,15,Ffrozen, morale is low.
OL,17,F"Yet colleagues in our school continue
OL,18,Fto deliver with less and less and
OL,19,Funder increasing pressure. I'm very
OL,20,Fconcerned that we are close to
OL,21,Fbreaking point."
