OL,5,Cyears ` poll
OL,7,FThe IOP is calling on the Government
OL,8,Fto commit funding for science and
OL,9,Fengineering departments, to set up an
OL,10,F"early warning system" for departments
OL,11,Fat risk of closure, and to radically
OL,12,Freform higher education funding.
OL,14,FIt also called for the Government to
OL,15,Fchange visa policy so international
OL,16,Fstudents were removed from net
OL,17,Fmigration figures, the graduate visa
OL,18,Fwas retained in its current form, and
OL,19,Fto make the Global Talent and Skilled
OL,20,FWorker visas more affordable.
